      "role": "user",
      "content": "that decline you mentioned with working-class men though... isn't there a lot of evidence that the increased benefits and government assistance are actually what's discouraging them from looking for work? people seem to say it creates this dependency where it's just not worth it to take a job if you'll lose your benefits.",
